WEBVTT

00:01.001 --> 00:03.337
[♪ pop music playing]

00:45.254 --> 00:48.966
PERFECT CROWN

00:59.851 --> 01:00.978
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

01:01.061 --> 01:02.980
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

01:03.063 --> 01:07.067
[clamoring]

01:07.150 --> 01:08.485
64TH ARCHERY EXHIBITION MATCH

01:08.569 --> 01:10.821
[scorekeeper] Hyeonmu House,
Black Tortoise of the North!

01:10.904 --> 01:12.364
[cheering]

01:12.447 --> 01:14.950
Cheongnyong House,
Azure Dragon of the East!

01:15.033 --> 01:16.451
[cheering]

01:21.331 --> 01:23.333
Jujak House, Vermilion Bird of the South!

01:23.417 --> 01:25.544
[cheering]

01:30.882 --> 01:32.968
Baekho House, White Tiger of the West!

01:33.885 --> 01:35.220
That brat is Jujak's rep?

01:36.388 --> 01:38.098
She's pretty good. I saw her practice.

01:38.807 --> 01:41.560
I got this key from Ryu Minseok,
Cheongnyong House, ninth grade.

01:42.603 --> 01:44.271
[Minseok] She is one vicious brat.

01:44.354 --> 01:47.107
Just last month,
she couldn't even break a seven.

01:47.899 --> 01:49.901
Why are you always so hostile toward her?

01:49.985 --> 01:51.320
Do you like her?

01:51.945 --> 01:54.323
[scoffs] A lowly creature like her?

01:55.407 --> 01:57.034
-Are you insane?
-[I-AN] Ryu Minseok.

01:57.117 --> 01:58.410
Yes?

01:59.036 --> 02:00.203
Watch your mouth.

02:01.121 --> 02:03.040
-Pardon?
-Your vulgarity…

02:04.833 --> 02:06.418
offends my eyes and ears.

02:10.255 --> 02:11.256
Understood.

02:16.720 --> 02:18.847
[cheering]

02:18.930 --> 02:21.516
[audience members]
Let's go, Cheongnyong House!

02:21.600 --> 02:23.352
[♪ tense music plays]

02:23.435 --> 02:25.228
Good luck!

02:35.739 --> 02:37.491
Ten points!

02:43.163 --> 02:44.581
Nine points!

02:45.248 --> 02:46.708
[screams]

02:46.792 --> 02:48.835
[chuckles]

02:49.795 --> 02:50.837
My goodness.

02:50.921 --> 02:53.590
The students' enthusiasm
is truly remarkable, isn't it?

02:54.174 --> 02:57.260
News of Your Majesty's attendance
really fired them up. [chuckles]

02:57.928 --> 02:59.137
Word has reached me

02:59.805 --> 03:01.723
that the archery range was open
around the clock.

03:01.807 --> 03:03.266
Yes, Your Majesty.

03:03.850 --> 03:06.687
It was a personal request
from Grand Prince I-AN.

03:08.271 --> 03:10.857
-[drum booming]
-[cheering]

03:19.449 --> 03:21.993
[audience members]
Cheongnyong House, you're so cool!

03:22.077 --> 03:24.287
-Go, Cheongnyong House!
-Cheongnyong!

03:24.371 --> 03:27.999
-Cheongnyong of the East!
-Cheongnyong of the East!

03:28.959 --> 03:30.961
[♪ determined music plays]
STYLE
::cue()

03:45.517 --> 03:47.018
[scorekeeper] Nine points!

03:47.102 --> 03:49.271
[cheering]

04:00.198 --> 04:01.199
Come on…

04:05.662 --> 04:07.247
[scorekeeper] Ten points!

04:08.290 --> 04:09.291
[sighs]

04:15.088 --> 04:17.757
[cheering]

04:19.176 --> 04:21.178
It's okay. We still have one more round.

04:22.137 --> 04:23.472
We can turn it around then.

04:35.066 --> 04:36.985
HYEONMU, CHEONGNYONG,
JUJAK, BAEKHO

04:37.819 --> 04:40.530
It appears victory belongs to
House Cheongnyong this year.

04:41.239 --> 04:42.532
I am not so sure.

04:42.616 --> 04:43.909
It is not over

04:44.951 --> 04:46.286
until it is truly over.

04:48.872 --> 04:50.707
[scorekeeper] Last round!

04:52.626 --> 04:53.627
[exhales sharply]

04:55.420 --> 04:57.005
[audience member] You got this!

04:57.088 --> 04:59.508
-Go, Cheongnyong!
-Go, Jujak!

04:59.591 --> 05:00.759
You got this, Jujak!

05:01.384 --> 05:02.677
[cheering]

05:09.017 --> 05:10.519
[audio fades]

05:10.602 --> 05:13.563
[♪ determined music plays]

05:34.459 --> 05:35.919
[scorekeeper] Nine points!

05:36.002 --> 05:37.838
JUJAK: 110 POINTS

05:53.228 --> 05:55.063
-[arrow thuds]
-[cheering]

06:05.490 --> 06:07.284
EPISODE 2

06:10.203 --> 06:11.371
Let's…

06:12.581 --> 06:13.582
get married.

06:16.001 --> 06:17.294
[chuckles]

06:46.656 --> 06:47.866
What are the terms?

06:48.783 --> 06:49.951
You don't seem surprised.

06:50.035 --> 06:51.244
[chuckles]

06:51.328 --> 06:52.329
Why should I be?

06:52.412 --> 06:55.081
-There must've been plenty before me.
-There have.

06:55.165 --> 06:58.501
Just in the past two days,
I've received dozens of match proposals.

07:05.425 --> 07:06.718
[sighs] Damn it.

07:11.014 --> 07:12.098
So…

07:13.933 --> 07:15.060
state your terms.
STYLE
::cue()

07:19.439 --> 07:21.691
I shall personally assess them.

07:24.194 --> 07:25.195
[scoffs]

07:28.448 --> 07:29.616
[clears throat, sighs]

07:31.826 --> 07:32.911
I have a lot of money.

07:35.163 --> 07:36.164
[chuckles]

07:37.582 --> 07:39.876
[laughing]

07:43.588 --> 07:46.007
I was expecting something
a little more creative.

07:46.091 --> 07:48.009
No point in wasting creativity.

07:48.093 --> 07:50.136
Arranged marriages are all the same.

07:51.763 --> 07:52.764
After all,

07:54.557 --> 07:56.726
familiarity makes everything feel better,

07:57.310 --> 07:59.771
from the food you eat,
to the path you take,

08:00.522 --> 08:01.815
even the clothes you wear.

08:03.024 --> 08:04.943
That's why you reach for them.

08:06.027 --> 08:07.529
[chuckles]

08:08.279 --> 08:09.280
[chuckles]

08:11.449 --> 08:12.450
So?

08:13.159 --> 08:14.619
An assessment of the familiarity.

08:15.412 --> 08:17.872
My pedigree is impressive,
and my acumen sharper still.

08:18.373 --> 08:19.874
I have an older brother,

08:20.583 --> 08:21.835
but you don't need to worry.

08:21.918 --> 08:25.004
He's too dumb to cause any trouble.

08:28.091 --> 08:30.468
I know you don't like it
when in-laws overstep.

08:32.220 --> 08:33.221
What else?

08:35.682 --> 08:36.891
[sighs]

08:37.559 --> 08:38.727
[chuckles]

08:40.019 --> 08:41.062
[inhales sharply]

08:41.146 --> 08:42.272
I've got thick skin.

08:43.565 --> 08:46.609
A successful woman and the bastard heir
to a conglomerate empire.

08:47.902 --> 08:50.697
Do you have any idea
how much criticism I face every day?

08:50.780 --> 08:54.117
Your Royal Highness
would never know in a million years.

08:54.200 --> 08:55.577
It's better that way.

08:56.828 --> 08:59.080
And I will make sure you never find out.

09:00.290 --> 09:01.374
So just use me

09:02.375 --> 09:03.626
as your human shield.

09:06.337 --> 09:08.423
Pew…

09:08.506 --> 09:09.674
-[clicks tongue]
-[grunts]

09:10.425 --> 09:11.926
[chuckles]

09:13.595 --> 09:16.389
We're getting divorced
once the contract is over anyway.

09:17.348 --> 09:18.725
And even then,

09:20.143 --> 09:21.144
I'll take the hit.

09:22.604 --> 09:23.605
[scoffs]

09:27.484 --> 09:28.610
Anything else?

09:32.864 --> 09:33.865
Beauty?

09:33.948 --> 09:34.949
[chuckles]

09:35.867 --> 09:36.868
What else?

09:37.786 --> 09:40.080
-You need more?
-Yeah. What else?

09:41.289 --> 09:42.290
[sighs]

09:45.210 --> 09:46.252
[grunts]

09:50.381 --> 09:51.549
-Areum?
-[gasps]

09:53.009 --> 09:55.136
-Aide Choi.
-What are you doing here?

09:55.762 --> 09:58.598
Well, it's time for his herbal tonic.

09:58.681 --> 09:59.891
[gasps]

09:59.974 --> 10:01.017
Such perfect timing.

10:01.101 --> 10:03.019
I can bring it to him. Give it to me.

10:03.728 --> 10:04.896
Ah…

10:06.940 --> 10:08.650
Your Royal Highness, it is Hyeon.

10:15.365 --> 10:16.574
[sighs]

10:21.913 --> 10:23.456
I-I have your tonic--

10:23.540 --> 10:25.208
-Leave it there and go.
-Yes, sir.

10:26.292 --> 10:28.294
[♪ suspenseful music plays]

10:30.213 --> 10:32.632
[door opens, closes]
STYLE
::cue()

10:51.192 --> 10:52.569
[court lady] Your Majesty.

10:52.652 --> 10:55.196
Jaegyeong of the Kim Family has arrived.

10:58.700 --> 10:59.701
Show her in.

11:20.680 --> 11:24.350
PERFECT CROWN

11:24.434 --> 11:26.144
CASTLE BEAUTY

11:26.769 --> 11:28.521
-Has Ms. Seong come in yet?
-What?

11:28.605 --> 11:29.772
Yes, she just came in.

11:31.232 --> 11:32.650
[humming]

11:35.737 --> 11:36.738
[knocks on door]

11:37.989 --> 11:39.157
[chuckles]

11:40.408 --> 11:43.036
What is it? Why are you smiling?

11:43.995 --> 11:45.747
You don't even like me smiling now?

11:46.456 --> 11:48.458
You shouldn't be smiling right now.

11:48.541 --> 11:51.044
Have you lost your mind?
Or are you being punished?

11:51.669 --> 11:52.670
-[chuckles]
-[gasps]

11:53.630 --> 11:56.007
Is he going to force you to drink poison?

11:56.090 --> 11:57.300
[scoffs]

11:57.383 --> 11:58.593
Don't be ridiculous.

11:58.676 --> 12:00.094
This isn't the Joseon Dynasty.

12:00.595 --> 12:01.888
Ah…

12:01.971 --> 12:02.972
Exactly.

12:03.556 --> 12:05.892
So what happened? Update me already.

12:06.476 --> 12:07.518
[sighs]

12:09.187 --> 12:10.188
I was rejected.

12:11.356 --> 12:12.398
What?

12:14.817 --> 12:15.944
I said I was rejected.

12:16.986 --> 12:18.029
[I-AN] I decline.

12:19.489 --> 12:21.449
-May I ask why?
-Because there is…

12:22.784 --> 12:26.162
[sighs] …something I value more
than wealth, ability, and beauty.

12:26.246 --> 12:27.622
And what might that be?

12:27.705 --> 12:28.706
If I tell you,

12:30.458 --> 12:31.542
can you give it to me?

12:31.626 --> 12:32.835
[chuckles]

12:33.711 --> 12:34.879
You think I can't?

12:37.173 --> 12:38.174
[scoffs]

12:38.258 --> 12:40.510
So? What did he say he needs?

12:42.553 --> 12:43.680
Love.

12:44.597 --> 12:45.598
Huh?

12:45.682 --> 12:47.267
He wishes to marry for love.

12:48.142 --> 12:49.352
[scoffs]

12:49.435 --> 12:51.771
It's been his lifelong dream, apparently.

12:52.814 --> 12:54.524
-[sighs]
-[mutters]

12:54.607 --> 12:56.693
He's more of a romantic than you'd think.

12:57.360 --> 12:59.612
-Romantic, my foot.
-You scared me.

12:59.696 --> 13:01.489
He's clearly just screwing with me.

13:02.615 --> 13:04.367
[Hyeon] So you screwed her over.

13:05.201 --> 13:07.203
I thought you two went to the same school.

13:07.745 --> 13:11.040
You could've just said no
and politely declined her offer.

13:11.124 --> 13:12.333
You should've been nicer.

13:12.417 --> 13:13.543
You can be so mean.

13:16.129 --> 13:17.130
[chuckles]

13:17.213 --> 13:19.215
[Ms. Do] I'll look for another candidate.

13:19.841 --> 13:20.842
Why?

13:22.093 --> 13:23.928
Since you were rejected.

13:24.012 --> 13:25.305
So?

13:25.388 --> 13:28.182
What? Are you going to try again?

13:28.266 --> 13:29.392
Yeah.

13:29.892 --> 13:31.936
Why? You weren't even sincere about it.

13:32.020 --> 13:34.355
Oh, please. I couldn't be more sincere.

13:34.439 --> 13:35.523
As if.

13:35.606 --> 13:37.108
What kind of "sincere" person

13:37.191 --> 13:40.028
would say, "I've got money, power,
a deadbeat brother,

13:40.111 --> 13:42.530
and I'll even sign the divorce papers"?

13:42.613 --> 13:44.282
Not a shred of modesty to be found.

13:44.782 --> 13:45.783
Ms. Do.

13:46.743 --> 13:51.664
Prince I-AN is already surrounded
by a horde armed with calculated modesty.

13:51.748 --> 13:54.751
What do you think it'll take
to win against them?

13:56.461 --> 13:59.130
You need a strategy to set yourself apart.

13:59.714 --> 14:00.757
[sucks teeth]

14:00.840 --> 14:01.841
[scoffs]

14:02.550 --> 14:05.970
So are you saying
you intentionally pulled that crazy stunt?

14:06.054 --> 14:09.724
I'm sure he's fond of eccentrics like me.

14:09.807 --> 14:11.851
Birds of a feather flock together.

14:13.186 --> 14:17.065
He showed up to His Majesty's
Royal Birthday Banquet in a cheollik.

14:17.148 --> 14:18.983
That's not "normal," is it?

14:20.401 --> 14:23.696
Were you not set
on Jaegyeong of the Kim Family?
STYLE
::cue()

14:23.780 --> 14:24.906
PROSPECTIVE CONSORT

14:24.989 --> 14:26.532
I do not intend to play matchmaker.

14:28.785 --> 14:30.369
I would rather remain a spectator.

14:33.456 --> 14:38.086
The more people interfere,
the greater the conflict grows.

14:38.669 --> 14:39.670
In the end,

14:40.838 --> 14:43.216
the one who staged it
will emerge the winner.

14:43.299 --> 14:44.634
Does that mean…

14:49.305 --> 14:50.973
I must meet this maiden.

14:54.310 --> 14:56.312
[♪ imposing music plays]

15:03.277 --> 15:04.487
[exhales sharply]

15:07.448 --> 15:09.617
You said to prepare the new proposal
by next week--

15:09.700 --> 15:11.410
-Listen…
-I'll have it by this evening.

15:11.994 --> 15:13.246
Mm-mmm.

15:13.996 --> 15:16.415
You can give that to me next week.

15:16.499 --> 15:17.500
Pardon?

15:18.292 --> 15:19.293
Then why…

15:20.044 --> 15:21.546
You do know…

15:22.380 --> 15:24.549
how much I rely on you,

15:25.633 --> 15:27.552
don't you? [giggles]

15:28.261 --> 15:30.513
[chuckles] M-Me? Y-You rely on me?

15:31.806 --> 15:32.807
[chuckles]

15:34.058 --> 15:35.893
I am aware.

15:35.977 --> 15:38.229
With that in mind,

15:39.147 --> 15:42.024
may I ask a small, secret favor

15:42.608 --> 15:43.985
of you?

15:44.068 --> 15:46.529
A secret favor?

15:46.612 --> 15:48.030
Secret.

15:48.781 --> 15:49.782
[giggles]

15:58.374 --> 15:59.792
W-W-Why? What's wrong?

15:59.876 --> 16:02.503
You're so out of it.
What are you even looking at?

16:03.379 --> 16:05.173
What did she say?

16:06.382 --> 16:08.634
-She's getting married.
-Huh?

16:08.718 --> 16:09.760
[gasps]

16:09.844 --> 16:11.137
[inhales sharply]

16:15.725 --> 16:18.394
Right… Wait, she's getting married?

16:18.477 --> 16:19.520
Mom.

16:20.062 --> 16:23.024
You know that uncle
you mentioned last time?

16:23.107 --> 16:24.192
Yeah.

16:24.275 --> 16:26.402
Not the one who went to jail.
I don't like him!

16:27.445 --> 16:28.696
[passerby clears throat]

16:30.281 --> 16:32.575
The one who works
at the Royal Secretariat.

16:32.658 --> 16:33.701
Yes, that's right.

16:34.202 --> 16:36.746
Do you think I could get
his contact information?

16:37.330 --> 16:38.956
[line ringing]

16:39.040 --> 16:40.291
Goodness, Reporter Park.

16:40.374 --> 16:42.084
It's me. Have you been well?

16:42.168 --> 16:43.169
Yes, of course.

16:44.128 --> 16:46.130
No, Ms. Seong is doing very well.

16:46.214 --> 16:47.381
Yes, that's right.

16:47.965 --> 16:51.344
So, Reporter Kim,
I heard you are a royal correspondent.

16:51.427 --> 16:52.970
Ah, in that case,

16:53.596 --> 16:56.933
you must have connections
with the Public Affairs Office as well.

16:57.016 --> 16:58.351
Ah…

16:58.434 --> 17:00.102
Yes, that's right. [chuckles]

17:01.312 --> 17:04.023
[inhales sharply]
He's taking some time off,

17:04.106 --> 17:05.608
so no official engagements.

17:05.691 --> 17:08.653
The Royal Guard
accompanies him for all that,

17:08.736 --> 17:11.906
-so he'd be impossible to approach.
-Is that so?

17:12.406 --> 17:13.491
However,

17:14.158 --> 17:16.744
he's bound to have informal engagements.

17:16.827 --> 17:19.956
As it turns out, there are a few spots
he visits frequently.

17:20.039 --> 17:22.375
-[laughs]
-[chuckles]

17:28.589 --> 17:30.383
I've managed to compile

17:31.759 --> 17:32.885
a comprehensive list.

17:33.511 --> 17:34.637
[sighs]

17:36.430 --> 17:38.641
-Thank you. I'll let you get back to work.
-[chuckles]

17:39.642 --> 17:41.018
W-Wait, Ms. Do.

17:44.021 --> 17:45.147
[mutters, sighs]

17:46.315 --> 17:49.026
Am I part of Ms. Seong's circle now?

17:49.110 --> 17:50.194
[chuckles]

17:51.737 --> 17:53.364
Of course.

17:53.447 --> 17:54.615
Without a doubt.

17:56.784 --> 17:57.868
Ah…

18:02.331 --> 18:04.041
[gasps, sighs]
STYLE
::cue()

18:06.419 --> 18:08.754
[horse whinnies]

18:08.838 --> 18:10.840
[♪ upbeat music plays]

18:18.806 --> 18:19.807
Hyah!

18:21.475 --> 18:22.893
[horse whinnies]

18:28.524 --> 18:30.026
-Whoa, whoa…
-[horse whinnies]

18:31.110 --> 18:32.111
[sighs]

18:36.282 --> 18:37.783
[sighs]

18:41.621 --> 18:43.748
-[horse whinnies]
-Hmm?

18:46.876 --> 18:48.377
[♪ upbeat pop music plays]

18:48.461 --> 18:49.795
Hyah!

18:49.879 --> 18:50.880
Hyah!

18:52.548 --> 18:53.674
Seong Huiju?

18:56.719 --> 18:57.845
[Huiju] Hyah!

19:01.641 --> 19:02.850
Whoa…

19:04.393 --> 19:05.394
[sighs]

19:06.187 --> 19:08.189
It's been a while, Your Royal Highness.

19:09.315 --> 19:10.775
I believe it has been two days.

19:10.858 --> 19:11.901
Isn't it odd?

19:12.401 --> 19:14.737
It's only been two days,
but I missed you so much.

19:16.656 --> 19:19.617
Why ride here
and not at the Royal Riding Grounds?

19:19.700 --> 19:21.035
It is too confined there.

19:24.246 --> 19:25.956
You could feel confined here too.

19:30.461 --> 19:31.504
[clears throat]

19:32.171 --> 19:33.631
[clicks tongue] Hyah!

19:35.424 --> 19:37.343
-[horse whinnies]
-[chuckles]

19:37.968 --> 19:39.720
-[clicks tongue]
-[horse whinnies]

19:41.180 --> 19:42.181
Hyah!

19:58.656 --> 19:59.782
[clicks tongue]

19:59.865 --> 20:00.991
I missed you.

20:01.492 --> 20:03.953
Even though I saw you yesterday. [giggles]

20:04.036 --> 20:05.121
[scoffs]

20:07.665 --> 20:10.793
But why are you having breakfast here
and not the Royal Dining Hall?

20:12.336 --> 20:14.755
-I am taking some time off.
-Oh…

20:15.756 --> 20:17.133
Me too. [giggles]

20:21.011 --> 20:22.888
Are you off to volunteer
at the cat shelter?

20:22.972 --> 20:24.432
To see Taekwon and Taegeuk?

20:26.267 --> 20:28.144
You dared to run a background check on me?

20:28.227 --> 20:29.687
-Yes.
-"Yes"?

20:30.271 --> 20:32.064
You said you wanted to marry for love.

20:33.315 --> 20:34.316
So?

20:34.400 --> 20:35.651
So…

20:36.861 --> 20:38.237
that is why I dare

20:39.071 --> 20:40.072
to make a play

20:41.407 --> 20:42.867
for Your Royal Highness's heart.

20:43.659 --> 20:45.619
-[blows]
-[stammers]

20:47.163 --> 20:48.330
[giggles]

20:52.835 --> 20:53.836
[scoffs]

20:53.919 --> 20:55.838
[♪ upbeat music plays]

20:55.921 --> 20:57.131
[chuckles]

21:01.761 --> 21:02.928
[horn honks]

21:11.479 --> 21:12.938
[chuckles]

21:13.022 --> 21:14.982
I missed you!

21:15.065 --> 21:16.108
Where are you…

21:23.407 --> 21:24.408
[sighs]

21:26.827 --> 21:28.204
[giggles]

21:28.287 --> 21:30.206
You can enjoy the movie.
STYLE
::cue()

21:31.499 --> 21:33.542
I'll just enjoy watching you.

21:36.670 --> 21:37.671
[sighs]

21:48.682 --> 21:49.892
I missed you.

21:50.684 --> 21:51.769
Should we run together?

21:54.230 --> 21:55.231
Oh!

22:00.945 --> 22:02.196
You're pretty fast!

22:02.822 --> 22:03.823
[pants]

22:10.496 --> 22:12.331
-What do you think?
-About what?

22:12.915 --> 22:15.584
The outfit I am wearing right now.

22:15.668 --> 22:18.045
Well, it's not bad…

22:18.128 --> 22:20.256
"It's not bad"? That simply won't do.

22:20.339 --> 22:21.799
What do you mean?

22:22.383 --> 22:25.469
Just keeps popping up out of nowhere.

22:25.553 --> 22:28.013
What keeps popping up out of nowhere?

22:28.722 --> 22:30.057
I must have new garments made.

22:30.140 --> 22:31.642
What? All of a sudden?

22:31.725 --> 22:35.062
If I'm shadowed at every turn,
shouldn't I appear flawless at every step?

22:35.145 --> 22:36.647
Wait, so who's shadowing you?

22:37.147 --> 22:38.315
Get in.

22:38.399 --> 22:39.984
Am I just talking to myself?

22:43.612 --> 22:45.865
[yawns]

22:47.032 --> 22:48.033
[groans]

22:49.618 --> 22:52.538
[phone ringing]

22:52.621 --> 22:53.664
GREMLIN

22:53.747 --> 22:56.250
What a crappy way to start the day.

22:57.376 --> 22:58.377
[sucks teeth]

23:01.297 --> 23:02.298
What is it?

23:02.381 --> 23:04.592
[Gremlin] Huiju, you haven't forgotten
what today is, right?

23:04.675 --> 23:06.010
I definitely did.

23:06.093 --> 23:08.137
That's why I'm calling to remind you.

23:08.220 --> 23:10.431
You have your arranged date today.

23:11.432 --> 23:13.517
Listen, Dayeong…

23:13.601 --> 23:14.602
[chuckles]

23:14.685 --> 23:16.604
I guess Father has high hopes for today.

23:16.687 --> 23:20.941
He insisted that I go to your place
to help you with your outfit and makeup.

23:21.025 --> 23:24.153
I spent ages trying to talk him out
of putting that pressure on you.

23:24.236 --> 23:26.864
How incredibly thoughtful of you.

23:26.947 --> 23:28.365
I know, right?

23:28.449 --> 23:30.743
Huiju, do you think you'll need my help?

23:30.826 --> 23:32.453
I can head over there right now.

23:32.536 --> 23:35.039
Yeah, you should go.
She's going to need a lot of help.

23:35.122 --> 23:36.957
-Taeju?
-You heard that?

23:37.041 --> 23:38.042
-[gasps]
-[mutters]

23:38.125 --> 23:41.003
What are you doing?
Shouldn't you be at work by now?

23:41.086 --> 23:44.882
[chuckles] Huiju, I'll text you his number
and the meeting place again.

23:44.965 --> 23:45.966
Be sure to check!

23:46.050 --> 23:47.343
You know if you bail on him,

23:47.426 --> 23:50.012
you'll put both Father and me
in a tough spot, right?

23:54.266 --> 23:56.685
Geez, this damn Gremlin is unbelievable.

23:56.769 --> 23:57.770
[phone notification]

24:00.105 --> 24:03.776
[Dayeong] Father is threatening to shut
down Castle Beauty if you bail again,

24:03.859 --> 24:04.985
so watch out!

24:05.569 --> 24:06.820
P.S. Kim Yeonjun.

24:06.904 --> 24:09.365
Height, 180 cm.
I hear he's really handsome too.

24:09.448 --> 24:10.449
[sighs]

24:12.284 --> 24:14.495
-[line ringing]
-[sighs]

24:15.704 --> 24:16.789
[Huiju] Mr. Kim Yeonjun?

24:17.289 --> 24:19.541
My apologies for the last-minute changes.

24:19.625 --> 24:21.752
I wanted to take care of this quickly.

24:21.835 --> 24:24.171
Not at all. I know how busy you are.

24:26.757 --> 24:29.301
I heard a lot about you from my father.

24:30.260 --> 24:31.261
Really?

24:31.762 --> 24:32.763
Yes, I heard

24:33.347 --> 24:35.307
that you possess both beauty and brains.

24:37.893 --> 24:40.938
And that you have
a deep appreciation for art as well.

24:41.021 --> 24:42.982
Hmm… I do?

24:43.607 --> 24:46.068
Yes, don't you run an arts foundation?

24:46.151 --> 24:47.861
Brilliantly, might I add.

24:47.945 --> 24:48.988
Oh, that?

24:49.738 --> 24:51.991
That's for money laundering purposes.

24:52.950 --> 24:54.284
Brilliantly so.

24:55.577 --> 24:56.578
Pardon?
STYLE
::cue()

24:57.621 --> 24:58.622
[clicks tongue]

24:59.123 --> 25:00.249
You know.

25:00.332 --> 25:01.333
[chuckles]

25:04.670 --> 25:06.505
When should we hold the wedding?

25:07.297 --> 25:09.174
September? October?

25:09.258 --> 25:11.301
[clears throat, coughs]

25:13.387 --> 25:14.930
[clears throat] Pardon?

25:15.014 --> 25:17.349
It's an arranged marriage anyway.

25:17.433 --> 25:18.934
No reason to prolong it.

25:19.018 --> 25:20.102
I see.

25:21.770 --> 25:23.105
But shouldn't we at least--

25:23.188 --> 25:24.773
Do you have siblings?

25:25.899 --> 25:26.942
Only son?

25:27.735 --> 25:28.736
Yes, I am.

25:29.528 --> 25:30.529
I'm an only child.

25:30.612 --> 25:31.864
Mmm…

25:31.947 --> 25:32.948
That's nice.

25:33.991 --> 25:36.452
No siblings to fight over the inheritance.

25:39.413 --> 25:41.165
PRIVATE COLLECTION OF
GRAND PRINCE I-AN

25:49.298 --> 25:51.216
I have an older brother.

25:52.926 --> 25:54.511
You know Director Seong Taeju?

25:55.012 --> 25:57.514
Yes, I met him last time
at a shareholders' meeting.

25:57.598 --> 26:01.685
My father simply adores him.

26:01.769 --> 26:03.979
He'll likely succeed
my father as chairman.

26:04.730 --> 26:06.482
And you're a part of that plan.

26:07.399 --> 26:08.400
Me?

26:08.901 --> 26:10.110
How am I a part of that?

26:10.194 --> 26:11.904
He doesn't want to give me leverage.

26:12.905 --> 26:14.782
I'm already good at my job.

26:15.449 --> 26:18.327
He knows if I marry
into a powerful family on top of that,

26:18.410 --> 26:20.788
the first thing I'll do is
kick my brother to the curb.

26:22.206 --> 26:23.791
I see. [scoffs]

26:28.045 --> 26:30.130
PRIVATE COLLECTION OF
GRAND PRINCE I-AN

26:30.214 --> 26:32.508
Is he a cat lover or something?

26:39.515 --> 26:40.808
Do you think you can do it?

26:41.642 --> 26:43.977
-Pardon?
-If you're interested in marrying me,

26:44.645 --> 26:46.939
money must be what you're after.

26:47.898 --> 26:49.441
I can do that.

26:50.734 --> 26:52.653
Whatever sum you have in mind,

26:53.403 --> 26:55.364
I can give you far more than that.

26:56.615 --> 26:59.493
What about you? Can you do your part?

26:59.576 --> 27:02.121
Are you willing to devote
all of yourself to me…

27:09.253 --> 27:11.088
so I can get all the way to the top?

27:14.049 --> 27:15.050
[Hyeon] Ms. Seong?

27:16.260 --> 27:17.261
Aide Choi.

27:17.344 --> 27:19.721
-Hello.
-Hello there.

27:19.805 --> 27:21.473
You must be here for the exhibit.

27:21.557 --> 27:24.893
Yes. I wanted to see for myself
how impressive the Royal Collection was.

27:24.977 --> 27:26.770
I see. Is it to your liking?

27:27.437 --> 27:28.605
[sucks teeth]

27:28.689 --> 27:29.773
It's not bad.

27:29.857 --> 27:31.358
I'd steal a few if I could.

27:31.441 --> 27:33.777
Then you should go to basement level two.

27:33.861 --> 27:36.321
-The expensive stuff is there.
-[laughs]

27:36.405 --> 27:37.531
Aide Choi.

27:38.115 --> 27:39.241
Coming.

27:39.324 --> 27:40.617
Please excuse me.

27:40.701 --> 27:41.952
Enjoy the exhibit.

27:43.579 --> 27:44.580
[chuckles]

27:47.249 --> 27:50.043
I'm sorry. I should've introduced you.

27:54.298 --> 27:55.299
Huiju.

28:01.305 --> 28:03.307
[♪ contemplative music plays]

28:05.392 --> 28:07.394
I don't think this marriage would work.

28:09.980 --> 28:11.773
Not the least bit surprised.

28:13.400 --> 28:14.401
[scoffs]

28:16.695 --> 28:18.155
[sighs]
STYLE
::cue()

28:23.076 --> 28:24.286
[meows]

28:25.245 --> 28:27.623
-Who?
-Ms. Seong Huiju.

28:27.706 --> 28:29.207
The one who proposed to you.

28:30.375 --> 28:33.253
Gosh, as soon as you turned her down,

28:33.337 --> 28:34.880
she found herself a new man.

28:34.963 --> 28:37.466
She's so cool. So cool.

28:37.549 --> 28:38.967
-[chuckles]
-[scoffs]

28:39.635 --> 28:40.636
[clears throat]

28:41.887 --> 28:46.141
To be honest, I was worried she might be
one of the Queen Mother's people.

28:46.224 --> 28:47.601
You have quite the imagination.

28:48.268 --> 28:49.519
Her Majesty and Seong Huiju?

28:49.603 --> 28:51.229
Why not? It's a possibility.

28:51.313 --> 28:52.856
[scoffs] "Why not"?

28:54.733 --> 28:56.234
Move it more to the right.

28:57.611 --> 28:59.071
More to the right?

29:01.114 --> 29:02.115
Up.

29:02.199 --> 29:03.283
Down.

29:03.367 --> 29:05.243
Up, up, down.

29:06.828 --> 29:07.871
[chuckles]

29:07.955 --> 29:09.039
Original spot.

29:09.122 --> 29:10.207
[groans]

29:13.752 --> 29:16.797
My sister-in-law hails from a family
that has produced four queens.

29:18.882 --> 29:21.009
Few people truly grasp
how towering that pride

29:22.094 --> 29:23.512
and sense of superiority is.

29:24.846 --> 29:25.847
A person like her,

29:26.723 --> 29:28.767
colluding with Huiju, a mere commoner?

29:29.893 --> 29:30.894
[scoffs]

29:33.855 --> 29:36.191
[Hyeon] Who would win between the two?

29:38.568 --> 29:39.695
Well, you see…

29:39.778 --> 29:41.071
[sniffs, chuckles]

29:41.154 --> 29:42.906
I did a little digging into Ms. Seong.

29:42.990 --> 29:44.074
-Choi Hyeon.
-I mean,

29:44.157 --> 29:46.076
it wasn't a proper investigation
or anything.

29:46.159 --> 29:48.662
It was just a light inquiry.

29:50.080 --> 29:52.749
[sighs] You have to admit
it was a bit strange.

29:52.833 --> 29:55.002
She just showed up out of nowhere
and proposed.

29:55.085 --> 29:56.712
-So?
-I found that

29:56.795 --> 29:58.213
there was nothing special to note.

29:58.296 --> 30:01.383
She only leaves the house to go to work.

30:01.466 --> 30:03.593
She doesn't seem to have
too many friends either.

30:03.677 --> 30:06.221
She eats with her assistant
and goes to the movies with her.

30:06.304 --> 30:07.597
Wait!

30:07.681 --> 30:09.182
Maybe it's because of her temper?

30:10.058 --> 30:12.060
-Her temper?
-You didn't know?

30:12.144 --> 30:14.479
I heard she was known
for being a hothead in school.

30:14.563 --> 30:17.399
It's harder to find someone
who hasn't fought her. [laughs]

30:18.025 --> 30:19.026
[chuckles]

30:19.109 --> 30:20.986
I hear she never lost a fight either.

30:22.904 --> 30:23.905
Aren't you curious?

30:25.115 --> 30:26.116
About what?

30:26.199 --> 30:29.244
As you said,
the Queen Mother and Ms. Seong

30:29.327 --> 30:30.954
could not be any more different.

30:31.038 --> 30:33.915
Of course, if rank is in play,
the outcome is obvious.

30:33.999 --> 30:36.376
But strip away the hierarchy?

30:36.460 --> 30:38.170
It'll be like "Pow!" With a bit of…

30:38.253 --> 30:40.964
[imitating explosions]

30:43.300 --> 30:44.342
My apologies.

30:51.683 --> 30:53.977
[door opens, closes]

30:56.104 --> 30:58.398
[♪ contemplative music plays]

30:58.482 --> 30:59.566
[sighs]

31:14.706 --> 31:16.958
[Yun] Have you truly gone mad?

31:26.885 --> 31:30.097
I INTEND TO STEP DOWN
FROM THE THRONE…

31:30.680 --> 31:31.681
[breathes shakily]

31:48.532 --> 31:50.450
It will be better than dying.

31:50.534 --> 31:51.535
[gasps]

32:00.460 --> 32:02.295
It would be better to die.

32:07.134 --> 32:08.593
I would rather see you dead.

32:10.262 --> 32:11.555
[sighs]

32:18.395 --> 32:20.355
For the sake of the Crown Prince.

32:33.743 --> 32:34.744
My Queen.

32:49.426 --> 32:51.052
My Queen!
STYLE
::cue()

32:54.347 --> 32:56.266
-Fire!
-It's a fire!

32:56.349 --> 32:59.269
[clamoring]

33:18.997 --> 33:21.166
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

33:21.249 --> 33:23.793
-Your Majesty…
-[sobbing]

33:25.045 --> 33:26.296
Your Majesty…

33:27.422 --> 33:28.757
Your Majesty…

33:54.532 --> 33:56.117
Where is the Crown Prince?

33:56.743 --> 33:57.744
Huh?

33:58.578 --> 34:00.205
Where is my nephew…

34:02.332 --> 34:03.750
the heir to the throne?

34:06.294 --> 34:07.295
[gasps]

34:08.171 --> 34:09.673
[breathes shakily]

34:37.909 --> 34:38.952
[sighs]

34:46.793 --> 34:48.253
Did you sleep poorly again?

34:59.764 --> 35:02.183
You can't keep going without sleep.

35:09.858 --> 35:12.736
Do you know what you will
be doing today, Your Majesty?

35:13.403 --> 35:15.780
I am to present the Flowers of Honor.

35:16.364 --> 35:20.118
The recipients are your valued subjects
who lead the nation's industries.

35:20.744 --> 35:22.912
They are Your Majesty's trusty workhorses.

35:23.413 --> 35:24.414
Hence,

35:25.707 --> 35:27.626
you must carry yourself with dignity.

35:31.212 --> 35:33.089
When is I-AN set to return?

35:33.173 --> 35:35.342
I believe he is to return in four days.

35:37.260 --> 35:38.386
This is your opportunity.

35:38.470 --> 35:40.972
You must show the world
you can do it on your own.

35:41.056 --> 35:43.016
Without I-AN by your side.

35:43.725 --> 35:45.101
Do you understand?

35:47.395 --> 35:48.396
Yes.

35:53.193 --> 35:54.277
[Hyeon] He'll be fine, right?

35:54.778 --> 35:55.945
No, he won't.

35:56.029 --> 35:58.490
How can you say that? You're his uncle.

35:59.199 --> 36:00.492
I know because I'm his uncle.

36:01.576 --> 36:04.579
I know that my nephew is but a mere child.

36:05.205 --> 36:08.750
Then perhaps you can go
and lend him your support.

36:10.460 --> 36:13.088
-Why should I?
-You said he is just a child.

36:14.214 --> 36:15.632
Why are you sweating so much?

36:16.466 --> 36:17.550
Are you feeling unwell?

36:18.802 --> 36:20.595
[phone buzzes]

36:21.554 --> 36:23.890
Yes, I'm listening.

36:25.934 --> 36:28.186
All right, I get it.

36:30.271 --> 36:31.856
DOBBY

36:31.940 --> 36:34.567
[Ms. Do] You have to be
at the venue by 11,

36:34.651 --> 36:36.111
so no dawdling please.

36:36.194 --> 36:37.821
Have you eaten?

36:37.904 --> 36:40.365
You won't have time to eat,
so eat something beforehand.

36:40.907 --> 36:42.742
There will be reporters everywhere.

36:42.826 --> 36:44.411
A lot of eyes will be on you.

36:44.494 --> 36:46.079
You know if you cause a scene,

36:46.162 --> 36:47.872
I'll be stuck working all night, right?

36:48.915 --> 36:51.126
Your dry-cleaned outfit is on the hanger.

36:52.711 --> 36:54.087
No red.

36:58.174 --> 36:59.592
-No strong perfume.
-[sighs]

37:01.219 --> 37:02.220
[sucks teeth]

37:02.887 --> 37:06.015
-No flashy accessories. Got it?
-[exclaims]

37:06.808 --> 37:09.185
I bought you for this exact purpose.

37:09.269 --> 37:11.354
Don't even. I told you nothing flashy.

37:12.897 --> 37:14.190
Are we on a video call?

37:18.653 --> 37:19.738
[mutters]
STYLE
::cue()

37:37.380 --> 37:39.340
[clamoring]

37:43.762 --> 37:46.598
2025 ECONOMIC HONORS OF KOREA

37:50.518 --> 37:52.604
This is how they treat their honorees?

37:53.313 --> 37:55.648
Lower your voice.
There are lots of reporters around.

37:55.732 --> 37:58.860
Seriously? If anything,
they should be boosting my morale.

37:58.943 --> 38:00.195
Are they trying to crush it?

38:00.278 --> 38:02.947
His Majesty the King is coming.
What choice do we have?

38:03.031 --> 38:04.866
Right, so why did he need to be here?

38:04.949 --> 38:06.409
Just enjoy cookies at the palace.

38:06.493 --> 38:07.911
-Stop it.
-All right!

38:09.871 --> 38:11.164
[chuckles]

38:18.588 --> 38:19.839
[secretary] Your Majesty.

38:19.923 --> 38:21.800
You do not need to be nervous.

38:21.883 --> 38:25.011
You have us by your side. [chuckles]

38:25.678 --> 38:27.180
Would Your Majesty like a snack?

38:28.181 --> 38:31.935
Can we review the order
of the ceremony again?

38:32.644 --> 38:36.064
Looking at that
will only make you more nervous.

38:36.147 --> 38:38.900
Once you step up onto the podium,
we'll take care of everything.

38:39.818 --> 38:41.194
[secretary chuckles]

38:41.277 --> 38:42.278
[sighs]

38:42.904 --> 38:43.905
Your Majesty.

38:46.908 --> 38:47.909
Your Royal Highness.

38:52.163 --> 38:53.206
What brings you here?

38:54.749 --> 38:56.459
You dare stand in my way?

38:58.127 --> 38:59.462
No, I wasn't…

38:59.546 --> 39:01.714
Then do you stand in His Majesty's way?

39:11.683 --> 39:13.560
The aides have been
negligent in their duties.

39:15.144 --> 39:17.438
Both protocol and security
are woefully inadequate.

39:18.481 --> 39:20.149
My apologies, Your Royal Highness.

39:23.611 --> 39:26.614
INCOMING CALL

39:26.698 --> 39:28.741
[phone buzzing]

39:29.492 --> 39:30.493
[sighs]

39:36.916 --> 39:38.126
Your Majesty.

39:38.209 --> 39:39.502
[Yun] Uncle.

39:41.421 --> 39:43.464
I am scared, Uncle.

39:45.758 --> 39:47.051
[sighs]

39:50.597 --> 39:51.764
[sighs]

39:58.187 --> 39:59.272
Thus,

39:59.898 --> 40:03.151
I have come to fulfill my duty
as your loyal subject, Your Majesty.

40:05.528 --> 40:07.280
[indistinct chattering]

40:11.910 --> 40:15.330
[secretary] Announcing His Majesty!

40:16.289 --> 40:19.667
[camera shutters clicking]
STYLE
::cue()

40:48.571 --> 40:50.239
Take my hand, Your Majesty.

40:52.367 --> 40:54.369
[♪ uplifting music plays]

41:22.063 --> 41:24.190
Next, we have
the Global Entrepreneur Award.

41:24.273 --> 41:27.443
Chairman Park Jeseung.
Please give him a warm round of applause.

41:36.285 --> 41:39.288
Next, we have the Best Entrepreneur Award.

41:39.372 --> 41:43.418
Castle Beauty's Seong Huiju.

41:45.586 --> 41:49.007
Castle Beauty remains at the forefront
of the global K-beauty craze,

41:49.090 --> 41:52.927
showcasing Korea's advanced technology
and refined beauty.

41:53.011 --> 41:54.679
Guided by the slogan "Eco Beauty,"

41:54.762 --> 41:58.016
they remain dedicated
to creating eco-friendly products.

42:02.562 --> 42:03.563
Your Majesty.

42:04.063 --> 42:05.690
Can you place it on my head?

42:07.817 --> 42:08.901
Right here.

42:10.403 --> 42:11.404
[sighs]

42:14.532 --> 42:15.825
[applause]

42:18.161 --> 42:19.954
I am deeply honored, Your Majesty.

42:20.038 --> 42:21.205
[chuckles]

42:26.044 --> 42:27.503
The nation rejoices

42:28.379 --> 42:29.797
in the beauty of your talent.

42:32.884 --> 42:34.093
I missed you.

42:37.263 --> 42:39.307
Will there be a prize as well?

42:41.100 --> 42:42.727
I believe it is already on your head.

42:43.895 --> 42:45.897
This is from His Majesty.

42:46.606 --> 42:48.232
There is something else I would like

42:49.358 --> 42:50.735
from Your Royal Highness.

42:51.360 --> 42:52.361
[clears throat]

42:54.030 --> 42:55.031
[chuckles]

42:55.114 --> 42:57.450
[host] She is a young leader
representing the nation.

42:57.533 --> 43:01.162
CEO Seong Huiju.
Please give her a warm round of applause.

43:18.513 --> 43:19.514
[inhales sharply]

43:25.770 --> 43:26.771
[giggles]

43:27.939 --> 43:28.940
Ready?

43:35.279 --> 43:36.531
-Got it?
-Yes, got it.

43:36.614 --> 43:37.615
Okay.

43:39.617 --> 43:40.618
[sighs]

43:40.701 --> 43:43.913
"Hashtag Flower of Honor."

43:44.497 --> 43:46.249
"Best Company."

43:46.332 --> 43:48.417
"Castle Beauty."

43:48.501 --> 43:50.336
"Hashtag…

43:52.755 --> 43:55.174
Grand Prince I-AN."

43:57.677 --> 43:59.262
[chuckles] Let's go.
STYLE
::cue()

44:02.014 --> 44:03.099
PRIME MINISTER MIN JEONGWOO

44:03.182 --> 44:05.434
-[knocks on door]
-[Jeongwoo] Come in.

44:05.518 --> 44:07.353
[door opens, closes]

44:10.690 --> 44:11.691
Sir.

44:11.774 --> 44:13.526
The Economic Honors event went smoothly.

44:14.402 --> 44:15.403
Really?

44:16.112 --> 44:18.322
Our young Sovereign is all grown up now.

44:18.948 --> 44:21.242
Grand Prince I-AN accompanied him.

44:22.243 --> 44:23.953
-Isn't he on leave?
-Yes.

44:24.036 --> 44:27.165
It was a last-minute decision
after His Majesty made a personal request.

44:27.248 --> 44:28.708
Hmm…

44:33.045 --> 44:34.297
PRINCE I-AN'S
SURPRISE APPEARANCE

44:34.380 --> 44:35.506
AT 2025 ECONOMIC HONORS…

44:39.302 --> 44:42.013
CASTLE BEAUTY'S SEONG HUIJU
RECEIVES BEST ENTREPRENEUR AWARD

44:44.765 --> 44:45.766
[chuckles]

44:48.186 --> 44:50.062
-[grunts]
-Are you going somewhere?

44:50.146 --> 44:51.480
I'm clocking out.

44:51.564 --> 44:52.982
Already?

44:53.065 --> 44:54.066
I'm done.

44:58.446 --> 45:00.656
And maybe a bit quicker next time.

45:01.574 --> 45:02.575
Pardon?

45:02.658 --> 45:04.952
If you tell me after the fact,
where does that leave me?

45:07.038 --> 45:08.748
-My apologies, sir.
-[chuckles]

45:22.511 --> 45:23.888
Get back safely, Your Majesty.

45:24.472 --> 45:27.099
Are you not coming with me?

45:28.142 --> 45:30.228
I am still on leave.

45:31.896 --> 45:34.732
Your Majesty, the Queen Mother is waiting.

45:38.110 --> 45:39.153
[sighs]

45:49.830 --> 45:50.831
[chuckles]

45:59.298 --> 46:00.299
[sighs]

46:03.761 --> 46:04.762
Are you all right?

46:08.849 --> 46:10.017
[gasps] Take this.

46:11.352 --> 46:12.353
This too.

46:13.896 --> 46:16.774
-Wait, hold on. Give me that too.
-Why?

46:16.857 --> 46:19.777
Are you actually wearing that hat
to your hotel staycation?

46:19.860 --> 46:21.112
-Yeah.
-Seriously?

46:21.862 --> 46:22.905
[sighs]

46:22.989 --> 46:25.199
Don't tell people
you're the CEO of Castle Beauty.

46:25.283 --> 46:26.617
[scoffs]

46:26.701 --> 46:29.578
[chuckles] They all know already.

46:30.663 --> 46:32.415
Don't call me unless it's urgent.

46:32.498 --> 46:34.375
It's been ages since I've had time off.

46:35.001 --> 46:37.753
Me too. Me too.

46:37.837 --> 46:39.255
-Go.
-I'm off.

46:42.341 --> 46:43.342
Seong Huiju.

46:45.011 --> 46:46.095
Oh.

46:46.178 --> 46:47.179
Jeongwoo.

46:48.889 --> 46:49.974
[chuckles]

46:57.148 --> 46:58.441
Order everything.

46:58.524 --> 47:00.234
I am a winner of the Flower of Honor.

47:00.318 --> 47:02.236
It'll be my treat today. [chuckles]
STYLE
::cue()

47:02.320 --> 47:03.738
[chuckles]

47:03.821 --> 47:04.822
No.

47:04.905 --> 47:07.241
Let me treat you today
to congratulate you.

47:07.325 --> 47:09.118
I told you I'd treat you last time.

47:10.161 --> 47:12.913
Now that's an offer I never turn down.

47:12.997 --> 47:14.123
Score.

47:14.707 --> 47:15.958
[chuckles, inhales sharply]

47:17.626 --> 47:18.753
Hmm…

47:23.382 --> 47:26.510
Just take it off for the meal.

47:26.594 --> 47:27.678
Why?

47:28.262 --> 47:30.014
Jealous? [scoffs]

47:30.097 --> 47:31.766
It's embarrassing.

47:32.350 --> 47:33.768
You look like a giant pineapple.

47:33.851 --> 47:35.144
[chuckles]

47:35.227 --> 47:37.646
Are you sure
it's not a really pretty pineapple?

47:38.230 --> 47:39.315
Definitely not.

47:40.274 --> 47:41.275
[scoffs]

47:46.906 --> 47:48.115
[sighs]

47:57.333 --> 47:59.627
Moments like this remind me
you haven't changed at all.

47:59.710 --> 48:01.504
What do you mean?

48:01.587 --> 48:04.465
You used to get the Flower of Honor
all the time in school.

48:04.548 --> 48:07.426
For your grades and artwork…

48:09.220 --> 48:10.388
What else was there?

48:11.972 --> 48:13.099
Archery?

48:13.974 --> 48:15.393
Archery. [chuckles]

48:15.476 --> 48:17.478
[♪ upbeat music plays]

48:25.277 --> 48:27.279
-[sighs]
-[sighs]

48:27.363 --> 48:30.533
How were you even chosen
to represent Jujak House?

48:30.616 --> 48:33.369
-I had to change my grip yesterday…
-[groans]

48:34.286 --> 48:35.746
Activate your core.

48:36.831 --> 48:38.499
Chin down.

48:38.582 --> 48:39.583
Chest.

48:40.209 --> 48:41.210
Chest.

48:43.421 --> 48:44.422
Draw your bow.

48:50.094 --> 48:51.679
Shoulders back further.

48:55.850 --> 48:56.934
Right by your lips.

49:02.815 --> 49:03.816
Focus!

49:04.900 --> 49:06.527
Right. Focus.

49:07.820 --> 49:09.905
-[clears throat]
-I swear

49:11.240 --> 49:14.702
there will be hell to pay
if we lose because of you.

49:16.620 --> 49:18.330
-Focus!
-Huh?

49:19.248 --> 49:20.624
Right, focus.

49:21.125 --> 49:22.293
Keep pulling

49:23.377 --> 49:24.378
and shoot.

49:25.379 --> 49:29.258
Thank goodness
you were at least book smart.

49:29.842 --> 49:31.552
-Me?
-You're bad at everything else.

49:31.635 --> 49:34.096
[chuckles] Seriously? Me?

49:34.180 --> 49:37.933
You're not like running the country
into the ground or anything, right?

49:39.018 --> 49:40.728
If something feels off,

49:40.811 --> 49:43.481
don't be afraid to ask questions.
No need to feel embarrassed.

49:43.564 --> 49:45.024
Don't try to do it alone.

49:45.107 --> 49:46.275
All right.

49:46.984 --> 49:48.152
Just order already.

49:49.403 --> 49:50.404
[chuckles]

49:51.155 --> 49:53.782
Let's see here.

49:56.118 --> 49:59.121
What should I have?
STYLE
::cue()

50:03.042 --> 50:04.627
PHARMACY

50:07.004 --> 50:08.088
Hello.

50:08.172 --> 50:09.215
Welcome.

50:09.298 --> 50:12.009
What should someone take
if they have a really bad headache,

50:12.092 --> 50:14.470
a slight fever,
and keep breaking out in a cold sweat?

50:14.553 --> 50:16.555
Just a moment. I'll grab what you need.

50:16.639 --> 50:18.891
Okay. Please hurry.

50:19.892 --> 50:20.893
[sighs]

50:30.152 --> 50:31.153
[sighs]

50:39.537 --> 50:40.538
Your Royal Highness.

50:50.881 --> 50:51.882
Once the fever breaks,

50:51.966 --> 50:53.884
we should take you
to Royal Seoul Hospital.

50:53.968 --> 50:56.178
I think it'd be best
to have you checked out there.

50:57.513 --> 50:59.640
It's crawling
with the Queen Mother's brothers.

50:59.723 --> 51:01.392
Don't stir up trouble.

51:01.934 --> 51:04.144
[sighs] Understood.

51:04.228 --> 51:05.563
Have you notified my household?

51:06.313 --> 51:07.314
Yes.

51:07.398 --> 51:09.650
I told them you'd be
staying the night at a hotel.

51:09.733 --> 51:12.236
I didn't say anything
about you being sick. Don't worry.

51:16.699 --> 51:18.075
[sighs]

51:21.245 --> 51:23.038
[automated voice] The doors are opening.

51:23.831 --> 51:24.915
[sighs]

51:27.710 --> 51:29.545
SHE LOOKS SO DAMN GOOD

51:29.628 --> 51:32.423
Our stock is going to skyrocket tomorrow.

51:34.341 --> 51:35.384
Oh, my goodness.

51:35.467 --> 51:36.468
Oh, my.

51:37.094 --> 51:38.721
-Ms. Seong?
-Aide Choi?

51:39.263 --> 51:40.723
-Hello.
-Yes, hello.

51:51.025 --> 51:52.568
You don't need to worry too much.

51:53.444 --> 51:57.573
However, I do wonder
if he typically has trouble sleeping.

51:58.407 --> 51:59.408
Uh…

51:59.992 --> 52:03.245
Yes, he suffers from a bit of insomnia.

52:03.329 --> 52:06.749
[doctor] It's hard to recover from fatigue
if you can't sleep.

52:07.458 --> 52:09.918
Sleeping aids should help.

52:10.002 --> 52:12.296
Make sure he gets a prescription
and gets some sleep.

52:12.379 --> 52:13.714
All right. Thank you, doctor.

52:27.895 --> 52:29.146
Doctor.

52:29.730 --> 52:31.690
Thank you for coming at a late hour.

52:31.774 --> 52:33.359
[chuckles] No need to thank me.

52:34.151 --> 52:35.194
For the record,

52:36.362 --> 52:38.947
can we say I was the patient today?

52:39.615 --> 52:42.117
-Pardon?
-You know I get hurt all the time.

52:43.369 --> 52:44.995
You were here to see me

52:45.704 --> 52:47.539
and only me today.

52:48.540 --> 52:49.541
[chuckles]

52:51.251 --> 52:52.378
Understood, Ms. Seong.

52:52.461 --> 52:53.462
[chuckles]

52:54.129 --> 52:55.130
Get back safely.

52:55.798 --> 52:56.799
Take care.

53:01.345 --> 53:02.805
PRINCE I-AN'S
SURPRISE APPEARANCE

53:02.888 --> 53:04.223
AT ECONOMIC HONORS…

53:10.479 --> 53:11.897
[sighs]

53:13.190 --> 53:16.193
Did you forget I told you
to carry yourself with dignity?

53:16.819 --> 53:20.698
U-Uncle…

53:20.781 --> 53:22.366
Do not call him that!

53:27.830 --> 53:30.040
Please do not let it upset you.

53:30.791 --> 53:33.210
His Majesty is still very young.

53:36.463 --> 53:38.716
How truly contemptible.

53:39.675 --> 53:40.676
Pardon?

53:43.220 --> 53:45.264
I speak of that feeble bloodline.

53:47.266 --> 53:51.186
He was the very likeness
of the late king at that moment.

53:54.231 --> 53:55.816
It sends a chill down my spine.

53:57.818 --> 53:58.819
[sighs]

54:02.948 --> 54:04.908
Have you located I-AN?

54:04.992 --> 54:06.744
Yes, Your Majesty.
STYLE
::cue()

54:12.791 --> 54:13.792
Aide Choi.

54:14.460 --> 54:15.627
Ms. Seong.

54:15.711 --> 54:17.045
You need to eat.

54:18.797 --> 54:19.965
How about a sandwich?

54:20.466 --> 54:22.384
SUBWAY

54:24.803 --> 54:25.804
[sighs]

54:25.888 --> 54:26.930
[chuckles]

54:28.140 --> 54:30.392
I see you really like sandwiches.

54:30.476 --> 54:31.477
[both chuckle]

54:32.186 --> 54:33.187
Not exactly.

54:34.021 --> 54:37.399
I was so preoccupied earlier
that I didn't get a chance to eat.

54:37.483 --> 54:39.777
And this is really good.

54:39.860 --> 54:40.986
Eat up.

54:41.069 --> 54:43.197
I order this all the time
when I'm working late.

54:47.493 --> 54:48.744
Thank you.

54:48.827 --> 54:50.954
He was just
on the verge of collapse earlier.

54:51.038 --> 54:53.248
My mind went blank.

54:54.082 --> 54:55.792
You were a huge help.

54:55.876 --> 54:57.377
[chuckles]

54:59.505 --> 55:01.673
But wouldn't he be better off
returning to the palace?

55:01.757 --> 55:03.300
There are physicians at the palace.

55:03.383 --> 55:06.678
I'm sure that will be more comfortable
than staying in some hotel room.

55:12.184 --> 55:14.394
He despises being the center of attention.

55:15.103 --> 55:16.813
The physicians would freak out
if they knew.

55:16.897 --> 55:19.525
The Royal Medical Institution
would be on standby all day.

55:20.025 --> 55:22.986
The Royal Kitchen would be cooking
all sorts of soups and porridges.

55:23.070 --> 55:26.031
Royal Seoul Hospital would be the same.
It'd be worse if anything.

55:26.114 --> 55:27.241
As soon as he steps inside,

55:27.324 --> 55:30.953
photos will be taken,
and all kinds of rumors will spread.

55:31.912 --> 55:32.913
Hmm…

55:33.413 --> 55:34.581
[phone buzzes]

55:40.337 --> 55:41.338
Oh, no.

55:42.589 --> 55:43.715
-You need to go.
-What?

55:43.799 --> 55:46.343
The Queen Mother is here.

55:46.426 --> 55:48.345
-Get up.
-Who? Mother?

55:48.428 --> 55:50.764
You need to get out of here.
The Queen Mother…

55:50.847 --> 55:53.016
-Where can I hide you? Come on.
-What's going on?

55:53.100 --> 55:55.978
-Where are you taking me?
-You have to be quiet.

56:00.691 --> 56:03.610
You can do this. You got this, Choi Hyeon.

56:08.031 --> 56:10.867
-Your Majesty, what brings you by?
-Step aside.

56:11.743 --> 56:13.287
It is already quite late. Tomorrow…

56:16.707 --> 56:17.708
[sighs]

56:31.763 --> 56:33.765
[♪ intense music plays]

56:44.776 --> 56:46.528
Tell her I am not yet suitably attired

56:48.238 --> 56:49.448
and that she must wait.

57:13.263 --> 57:15.474
[breathes shakily, sighs]

57:24.358 --> 57:25.901
[sighs]

57:43.251 --> 57:45.504
When the day breaks,
get yourself suitably attired

57:45.587 --> 57:47.255
to answer for today's transgression.

57:50.384 --> 57:51.927
That is what you will tell him.

57:59.351 --> 58:00.560
What now?
STYLE
::cue()

58:09.027 --> 58:11.071
[phone ringing]

58:11.154 --> 58:13.615
[groans]

58:22.249 --> 58:24.418
-Yeah?
-[Ms. Do] Ms. Seong, where are you?

58:24.501 --> 58:27.879
Ms. Do, do you know
what time it is right now?

58:27.963 --> 58:29.131
Where are you?

58:30.173 --> 58:31.425
At the hotel.

58:31.508 --> 58:33.677
-Stay right there.
-What?

58:33.760 --> 58:35.804
Stay in your room. I'll come to you.

58:35.887 --> 58:36.888
Got it?

58:37.514 --> 58:38.640
[sighs]

58:38.724 --> 58:39.725
[line disconnects]

58:40.475 --> 58:41.977
What's wrong with her?

58:44.813 --> 58:46.648
[sighs]

58:46.732 --> 58:48.567
PRINCE I-AN SPOTTED
IN SECRET TRYST

58:48.650 --> 58:50.068
WITH CASTLE BEAUTY SEONG HUIJU

58:50.152 --> 58:52.696
[indistinct chattering]

58:52.779 --> 58:54.740
WHERE THE ROYAL COUPLE
ENJOYS THEIR TIME OFF…

58:56.116 --> 58:57.325
…A SECRET DATE AT A HOTEL…

58:57.409 --> 58:58.410
ROYAL PAIR ROCKS…

58:58.493 --> 59:00.328
PRINCE I-AN'S SECRET LOVER…

59:01.538 --> 59:03.039
[phone ringing]

59:03.123 --> 59:04.875
-No, no.
-[employee] Yes, Reporter Kim.

59:04.958 --> 59:07.711
-I'll get back to you.
-No, we haven't confirmed anything yet.

59:07.794 --> 59:09.796
-Yes, will do.
-No, not at all.

59:09.880 --> 59:11.173
-Just a moment.
-Hello?

59:11.256 --> 59:12.424
[exclaims]

59:12.507 --> 59:14.217
Is Seong Huiju insane?

59:14.301 --> 59:15.969
-Why? What's up?
-Look at this.

59:18.138 --> 59:19.181
WEDDING BELLS…

59:21.057 --> 59:22.517
[gasps, exclaims]

59:22.601 --> 59:24.102
Oh my goodness! [gasps]

59:25.228 --> 59:28.482
-Do you think they slept together?
-Of course, they were at a hotel!

59:28.565 --> 59:30.692
[chuckles, inhales sharply]

59:31.276 --> 59:32.736
Ooh…

59:32.819 --> 59:34.571
What are you so happy about?

59:34.654 --> 59:35.989
What? Are you jealous of her?

59:37.407 --> 59:39.242
You are unbelievable.

59:42.537 --> 59:45.832
Ah… Is that why
she turned down all those dates?

59:47.667 --> 59:48.877
You think so?

59:48.960 --> 59:51.046
[chuckles, scoffs]

59:51.630 --> 59:54.132
"Grand Prince I-AN's secret lover"?

59:55.926 --> 59:56.927
Me?

59:58.053 --> 59:59.805
[chuckles]

01:00:01.765 --> 01:00:05.268
Pull yourself together, Do Hyejeong.
You've been through far worse.

01:00:05.352 --> 01:00:06.728
You got this. Damn it.

01:00:06.812 --> 01:00:08.730
Calm down.

01:00:08.814 --> 01:00:10.148
Who'd believe this crap?

01:00:10.774 --> 01:00:12.734
Why wouldn't they?

01:00:12.818 --> 01:00:14.110
Ms. Seong.

01:00:14.194 --> 01:00:16.363
Look. They have photos.

01:00:17.197 --> 01:00:19.533
Prince I-AN checks in at 4:00 p.m. Snap.

01:00:19.616 --> 01:00:22.202
You check in at 7:00 p.m. Snap.

01:00:22.285 --> 01:00:23.411
You step out at 9:00 p.m.

01:00:23.495 --> 01:00:26.373
to return at 9:30 p.m.
with sandwiches. Snap.

01:00:26.456 --> 01:00:29.668
And you can even see
where you got the sandwiches from.

01:00:29.751 --> 01:00:31.211
-Really?
-Yes.

01:00:31.294 --> 01:00:34.256
Wow. That sandwich place
just hit the jackpot.

01:00:34.923 --> 01:00:36.883
They should pay us for the PR.

01:00:36.967 --> 01:00:38.468
-[chuckles]
-Ms. Seong.

01:00:39.594 --> 01:00:40.720
All right. I hear you.

01:00:41.346 --> 01:00:43.473
But I swear nothing happened.

01:00:44.057 --> 01:00:46.685
We were with Aide Choi and stuff.

01:00:46.768 --> 01:00:48.061
Oh, I see.

01:00:48.144 --> 01:00:51.231
Who cares about that
when Aide Choi isn't in a single shot?

01:00:51.314 --> 01:00:53.483
-Not even a single royal guard.
-[sighs]

01:00:53.567 --> 01:00:54.901
What a great narrative.

01:00:55.527 --> 01:00:57.988
"Prince I-AN Dismisses
Royal Guards for Secret Tryst."

01:00:58.071 --> 01:01:00.073
From the riding grounds

01:01:00.156 --> 01:01:01.741
to a traditional restaurant,

01:01:01.825 --> 01:01:04.077
all sorts of location shoots for you.

01:01:04.160 --> 01:01:05.954
-[phone buzzes]
-[Hyejeong sighs]

01:01:06.037 --> 01:01:07.581
SEONGSAN DAILY REPORTER
AN SAEHUN

01:01:10.917 --> 01:01:12.252
HAEMYEONG REPORTER JEONG SUJIN

01:01:12.335 --> 01:01:13.670
[chuckles]

01:01:17.007 --> 01:01:19.175
First of all,
why did you call for your doctor?

01:01:20.051 --> 01:01:21.094
They got him too?

01:01:22.345 --> 01:01:25.056
Thanks to that shot,
they're even speculating you're pregnant.

01:01:25.140 --> 01:01:26.933
What? [scoffs]

01:01:28.310 --> 01:01:29.311
Wow…

01:01:29.394 --> 01:01:32.022
You have to hand it
to the public's imagination.

01:01:32.105 --> 01:01:33.523
[chuckles]

01:01:33.607 --> 01:01:34.941
"A premarital pregnancy"?

01:01:35.567 --> 01:01:36.818
-Focus!
-[gasps]

01:01:38.278 --> 01:01:39.279
Focus.

01:01:39.905 --> 01:01:41.823
Are you sure it will be all right?

01:01:42.949 --> 01:01:45.201
I fear this may bring
dishonor to the Crown.

01:01:45.702 --> 01:01:47.245
I am sure it will.

01:01:48.204 --> 01:01:50.832
The royal family's dignity
will be cast to the ground…

01:01:53.376 --> 01:01:56.671
and this woman will be laid
upon the chopping block and carved up.

01:01:57.297 --> 01:01:58.298
That must be why…

01:02:00.425 --> 01:02:01.885
they are denying it.

01:02:07.974 --> 01:02:09.643
[Hyejeong] Are you doing this

01:02:09.726 --> 01:02:12.312
because you don't know
who Prince I-AN is for the people?

01:02:13.229 --> 01:02:15.732
Did you already forget last year
when you dated the leader

01:02:15.815 --> 01:02:18.777
of Idol Galaxy or whatever
and got egged when you were caught?

01:02:18.860 --> 01:02:20.445
They keyed your car every other day.

01:02:20.528 --> 01:02:23.573
You said it was pure torture
dealing with the overzealous fans

01:02:23.657 --> 01:02:25.575
who rang your doorbell at dawn
and ran away.

01:02:25.659 --> 01:02:27.035
You must remember that.

01:02:28.119 --> 01:02:29.120
[clicks tongue]

01:02:29.204 --> 01:02:30.872
Prince I-AN isn't an idol star.

01:02:31.623 --> 01:02:33.249
He's so much worse.

01:02:33.333 --> 01:02:36.211
Idol stars are beloved
by their fandom alone.

01:02:36.294 --> 01:02:39.089
Prince I-AN is beloved
by the whole country.

01:02:39.172 --> 01:02:40.173
Everyone.

01:02:40.256 --> 01:02:41.633
[scoffs]

01:02:41.716 --> 01:02:42.717
I don't love him.

01:02:42.801 --> 01:02:44.010
-Ms. Seong!
-[gasps]

01:02:45.345 --> 01:02:47.514
You're going to scare the baby!

01:02:49.265 --> 01:02:50.600
[chuckles]

01:02:50.684 --> 01:02:52.852
"A premarital pregnancy"? [chuckles]

01:02:52.936 --> 01:02:54.062
Unbelievable.

01:02:55.188 --> 01:02:56.982
Right. Got it.
STYLE
::cue()

01:02:58.149 --> 01:03:01.152
[♪ imposing music plays]

01:03:02.779 --> 01:03:04.155
[line ringing]

01:03:09.327 --> 01:03:10.328
GRAND PRINCE

01:03:10.412 --> 01:03:12.038
SEONG HUIJU

01:03:13.248 --> 01:03:14.624
[line ringing]

01:03:15.291 --> 01:03:17.544
[automated voice]
The caller is unavailable…

01:03:18.878 --> 01:03:19.879
[line disconnects]

01:03:19.963 --> 01:03:21.381
Sir.

01:03:21.464 --> 01:03:23.842
Still, wouldn't it be best
to contain this quickly?

01:03:23.925 --> 01:03:26.386
If people start throwing around
terms like "Royal Risk"…

01:03:26.469 --> 01:03:28.805
-It won't be all bad.
-Pardon?

01:03:28.888 --> 01:03:32.350
It'll make all the criticism
over the minimum wage freeze disappear.

01:03:32.892 --> 01:03:35.395
Leave it for now. It's just a minor fuss.

01:03:36.187 --> 01:03:37.188
[secretary 2] Yes, sir.

01:03:48.950 --> 01:03:50.452
[Hyeon] To the palace, please.

01:03:51.202 --> 01:03:52.454
To my private residence.

01:03:52.537 --> 01:03:53.538
[grunts]

01:03:53.621 --> 01:03:55.623
You need to make your way
to the palace first.

01:03:55.707 --> 01:03:57.459
Prime Minister Min is already there.

01:03:57.542 --> 01:03:59.461
The Public Affairs Office
is also looking--

01:03:59.544 --> 01:04:01.337
I said, to my private residence.

01:04:03.757 --> 01:04:05.216
Have Seong Huiju…

01:04:05.925 --> 01:04:07.093
meet me there.

01:04:42.796 --> 01:04:43.880
[sighs]

01:04:47.467 --> 01:04:48.802
[chuckles]

01:04:53.389 --> 01:04:55.350
-This way, Ms. Seong.
-[chuckles]

01:05:16.830 --> 01:05:18.206
Am I the only one freaking out?

01:05:18.957 --> 01:05:21.084
No. I'm freaking out too.

01:05:28.508 --> 01:05:29.801
[Hyeon] Only Ms. Seong may go inside.

01:05:29.884 --> 01:05:32.345
His Royal Highness asked
for a private meeting.

01:05:35.014 --> 01:05:37.267
I'm fine. Just wait for me here.

01:05:37.350 --> 01:05:38.351
[clicks tongue]

01:05:43.314 --> 01:05:44.649
[Hyejeong groans]

01:05:51.865 --> 01:05:53.616
Is your fever gone?

01:05:55.618 --> 01:05:56.911
-As you can see.
-[chuckles]

01:05:58.371 --> 01:06:00.290
[chuckles] You're in good spirits.

01:06:01.124 --> 01:06:02.500
As you can see.

01:06:02.584 --> 01:06:03.710
[chuckles]

01:06:04.752 --> 01:06:07.172
I missed you.
Even though I saw you yesterday.

01:06:08.256 --> 01:06:09.299
[chuckles]

01:06:16.055 --> 01:06:17.223
Let me apologize

01:06:18.183 --> 01:06:19.809
for dragging you into this scandal

01:06:19.893 --> 01:06:22.562
and letting you become
the scapegoat for it.

01:06:23.396 --> 01:06:24.397
All of it.

01:06:27.066 --> 01:06:28.067
So?

01:06:29.569 --> 01:06:30.570
Tell me what you desire.

01:06:32.739 --> 01:06:33.865
[scoffs]

01:06:35.909 --> 01:06:36.910
If I tell you,

01:06:38.745 --> 01:06:39.746
can you give it to me?

01:06:39.829 --> 01:06:41.247
[chuckles]

01:06:41.331 --> 01:06:42.332
Seong Huiju.

01:06:42.415 --> 01:06:44.167
What I desire

01:06:45.335 --> 01:06:47.337
may be terribly difficult to attain.

01:06:52.759 --> 01:06:54.010
Let me get this straight.

01:06:54.093 --> 01:06:58.014
That woman and His Royal Highness
are actually an item?

01:06:58.097 --> 01:07:01.643
Didn't they seem like they had
nothing going on last time she visited?

01:07:01.726 --> 01:07:04.062
A secret rendezvous at a hotel?
That's a done deal.

01:07:04.145 --> 01:07:05.980
Still, don't you think it's a bit weird?

01:07:06.064 --> 01:07:07.941
His Royal Highness is so busy.

01:07:08.024 --> 01:07:09.817
When did he have time to date?

01:07:09.901 --> 01:07:10.944
Areum.

01:07:11.569 --> 01:07:13.196
I've told you a hundred times.

01:07:13.905 --> 01:07:16.449
When people say they can't date
because they're too busy,

01:07:17.283 --> 01:07:18.952
it's just an excuse.

01:07:32.840 --> 01:07:33.841
Do you remember?
STYLE
::cue()

01:07:36.010 --> 01:07:37.262
It's a Flower of Honor.

01:07:37.845 --> 01:07:39.514
The one I received after I beat you.

01:07:42.600 --> 01:07:44.310
[cheering]

01:07:57.782 --> 01:07:59.033
[scorekeeper] Seven points!

01:07:59.117 --> 01:08:01.119
[cheering]

01:08:13.715 --> 01:08:15.383
CHEONGNYONG: 109 POINTS

01:08:16.301 --> 01:08:17.510
[sighs]

01:08:26.978 --> 01:08:28.062
[scoffs]

01:08:28.146 --> 01:08:29.397
[Huiju] Didn't feel like crap?

01:08:32.442 --> 01:08:34.110
It felt like crap to me.

01:08:36.070 --> 01:08:38.197
Losing to someone

01:08:39.407 --> 01:08:40.450
who I could have beaten.

01:08:44.704 --> 01:08:45.705
[chuckles]

01:08:46.581 --> 01:08:48.291
My brother is an idiot.

01:08:49.375 --> 01:08:52.295
He got kicked out of the school
we made a donation to.

01:08:52.378 --> 01:08:55.548
He even managed to tank a business
that would've run on its own.

01:08:58.551 --> 01:09:00.345
But my father and the board

01:09:01.262 --> 01:09:03.973
are always dying to replace me with him

01:09:04.599 --> 01:09:07.018
whenever I make the slightest mistake.

01:09:08.269 --> 01:09:09.937
As if they've been biding their time.

01:09:11.189 --> 01:09:12.565
Why do you think that is?

01:09:14.067 --> 01:09:15.735
Because he was born before me?

01:09:15.818 --> 01:09:18.071
Because he's a son? And a legitimate heir?

01:09:21.032 --> 01:09:22.033
Oh…

01:09:23.409 --> 01:09:25.536
Perhaps it's because he married
into a noble family.

01:09:27.622 --> 01:09:28.873
That's why…

01:09:32.627 --> 01:09:34.420
I'm looking to marry up.

01:09:35.004 --> 01:09:36.172
[chuckles]

01:09:38.758 --> 01:09:40.551
You would marry me for nothing more

01:09:41.719 --> 01:09:42.929
than a hollow title?

01:09:43.012 --> 01:09:46.933
Because I've lost countless opportunities
simply for not having that title.

01:09:49.018 --> 01:09:51.562
[♪ soft music plays]

01:10:01.989 --> 01:10:04.909
Prepare yourself to become
the Grand Prince's wife.

01:10:13.209 --> 01:10:14.293
You will be up against…

01:10:16.087 --> 01:10:17.088
[chuckles]

01:10:17.797 --> 01:10:19.716
…the whole nation.

01:10:20.925 --> 01:10:22.927
[♪ music intensifies]

01:10:26.013 --> 01:10:27.014
[chuckles]

01:10:33.062 --> 01:10:34.230
[chuckles]

01:10:40.236 --> 01:10:43.156
PERFECT CROWN

01:11:19.275 --> 01:11:22.987
[journalist] Your Royal Highness,
is your scandal with CEO Seong Huiju true?

01:11:23.070 --> 01:11:26.282
The top five trending key words
are all about you.

01:11:26.365 --> 01:11:27.825
[Huiju] He's even a good actor.

01:11:27.909 --> 01:11:29.744
You're really going to marry him?

01:11:29.827 --> 01:11:31.996
I have to marry him right now.

01:11:32.079 --> 01:11:34.081
[student] Stay away
from His Royal Highness!

01:11:34.165 --> 01:11:36.125
She will be staying here
for the time being.

01:11:36.209 --> 01:11:38.169
[Yun] An investigation is required.

01:11:38.252 --> 01:11:41.047
[official] Cooperate with the Junghwajeon
Hall fire investigation, please.

01:11:41.130 --> 01:11:42.507
It's fine.

01:11:42.590 --> 01:11:45.092
[Huiju] I'm used to going up
against people like that.

01:11:45.176 --> 01:11:47.512
[I-AN] I must appear
insanely infatuated with you

01:11:48.805 --> 01:11:50.223
for people to believe

01:11:51.349 --> 01:11:53.184
this absurd marriage is genuine.

01:12:07.448 --> 01:12:09.075
PERFECT CROWN

01:12:09.158 --> 01:12:11.160
Translated by Justin S. Kim
